text: Syed Rahmatur Rob Irtiza Ahsan is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Barguna-2. ==Career== Ahsan was elected to parliament from Barguna-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. He contested the 1991 election as a candidate of National Democratic Party but lost to independent candidate Nurul Islam Moni. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:National Democratic Party (Bangladesh) politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
